# CHANGELOG

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

## [Unreleased]

- (Place upcoming features and fixes here!)

## [1.1.0] - 2025-07-26

### Added
- Expanded and updated the README.md to comprehensively cover all current features and usage instructions. [06878a0]

### Improved
- Enhanced UI elements for a better, more user-friendly experience. [6334772]

### Fixed
- Bug fixes and updates in app.py to improve stability and function. [55984fd]

## [1.0.0] - 2025-07-25

### Added
- Implemented a complete Telugu stories platform with interactive features:
    - Story card rendering with upvote and downvote functionality.
    - Full story view and social sharing capabilities.
    - Comprehensive form validation with real-time character counters.
    - Statistics dashboard with platform usage metrics.
    - Advanced search and filtering system.
    - Multi-page navigation system: home, write, stats, about.
    - Community guidelines page.
    - Fully responsive design for mobile and desktop.
    - Error handling and improved user interaction tracking. [e6cee6a]

### Changed
- Complete refactor: Overhauled the Telugu stories app codebase with OOP design.
    - Enhanced UI with modern CSS, animations, and responsiveness.
    - Refactored for better maintainability and code clarity.
    - Improved navigation, statistics tracking, error handling, and filtering.
    - Comprehensive form validation added.
    - Implemented upvote/downvote and sorting features. [bcb0c09]

